text: Dil Sambhal Jaa Zara was an Indian drama finite television series which broadcasted on Star Plus and was being produced by Bollywood filmmaker Vikram Bhatt.The Show Started Sanjay Kapoor and Smriti Kalra in lead roles.The Show went off air on 2nd February 2018 Due to Low Trp Ratings. Category:2017 Indian television series debuts
title: Dil Samabhal Jaa Zara
